Progress

Class Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • Progress.Graph
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OverviewTutorialGraph, StudentGraph

    public abstract class Graph
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class provides default implementations for most of the methods used for the graphs of students' progress and scores. It takes care of creating, editing, and displaying any type of graph needed.
